| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2116 — Recovery Inhibition (8base)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9ccfd08a-54f0-5bc7-bed3-b76b98d20c1c"
